---
title: Cajun Spiced Bass with Sweet Potato & Cavolo Mash with a Chive Dressing
description: We love good Cajun Spiced Bass and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cajun-spiced-bass-8422e3ab-7cd368ae.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/cajun-spiced-bass-5ec5259b7a987b0cec560b89-9134fa12.pdf
